From Michael Zyda Subject ACM SIGGRAPH Registration Problem A word of warning for those of you registering for SIGGRAPH ' I just received my registration form back in the mail with the envelope marked Return to Moved Left No Closed PO Box The address I used to register for SIGGRAPH ' is the one printed on the registration form ACM SIGGRAPH ' PO Box Chicago IL I printed the envelope in my best printing honest but evidently SIGGRAPH ' has skipped town or moved I ended up faxing my registration to I hope that number is real Michael Zyda